pageContext.claim: “The story in the @nytimes about the U.S. escalating attacks on Russia’s power grid is Fake News, and the Failing New York Times knows it. They should immediately release their sources which, if they exist at all, which I doubt, are phony. Times must be held fully accountable!”
pageContext.analysis: There’s no reason to believe the New York Times’s story was false. The Times did not retract or correct {the story} after Trump’s tweet.
